54
00:02:32,787 --> 00:02:35,037
the fecal sludge
treatment plant in Durban.

55
00:02:35,202 --> 00:02:37,465
These technologies are currently
in their research stage

56
00:02:37,633 --> 00:02:39,633
in preparation for scaling up.

57
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:43,195
So why do we distinguish
technologies as established

58
00:02:43,372 --> 00:02:45,797
transferring and innovative?

59
00:02:46,001 --> 00:02:49,001
The level of technology development
is and important indicator

60
00:02:49,173 --> 00:02:51,435
in selecting
an appropriate technology

61
00:02:51,634 --> 00:02:55,534
based on the level of adaption,
research, innovation, as well

62
