70
00:03:17,625 --> 00:03:18,675
are available.

71
00:03:19,194 --> 00:03:22,094
For transferring technologies
and innovative technologies

72
00:03:22,252 --> 00:03:24,014
the increased risk,
due to the lower level

73
00:03:24,188 --> 00:03:26,525
of technology development
needs to be considered

74
00:03:26,685 --> 00:03:29,048
and managed, this could be,
for example done through

75
00:03:29,219 --> 00:03:31,869
public private partnerships
or research collaborating

76
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,315
