Following the effluent from
this waste stabilization pond

141
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:38,572
is further treated in facultative

142
00:06:38,744 --> 00:06:40,644
and maturation waste
stabilization ponds

143
00:06:40,827 --> 00:06:42,602
and constructive wet lands.

144
00:06:42,834 --> 00:06:45,571
The solids that settle in anaerobic
waste stabilization ponds

145
